---
// src/pages/privacy.astro
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — ATEC Gurdaspur" noIndex={true}>
<style>
  .policy-hero { background:#0f2a5c; padding:56px 32px 44px; text-align:center; color:#fff; }
  .policy-hero h1 { font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:2rem; font-weight:900; margin:0 0 8px; }
  .policy-hero p { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size:14px; }
  .policy-body { max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; padding:56px 32px 80px; }
  .policy-body h2 { font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; font-size:1.2rem; font-weight:800; color:#0f2a5c; margin:32px 0 10px; }
  .policy-body p,.policy-body li { font-size:15px; color:#475569; line-height:1.8; margin:0 0 12px; }
  .policy-body ul { padding-left:20px; }
  .policy-body a { color:#0f2a5c; }
  .last-updated { background:#f8fafc; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:8px; padding:12px 16px; font-size:13px; color:#94a3b8; margin-bottom:32px; }
</style>
<div class="policy-hero">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>How we collect, use, and protect your information</p>
</div>
<div class="policy-body">
  <div class="last-updated">Last updated: June 2026</div>

  <p>ATEC Educational Society ("ATEC", "we", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we handle your personal information when you use our website at atecedu.com.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Enquiry forms</strong> — name, phone number, email, course interest</li>
    <li><strong>Account registration</strong> — name, email, phone, address</li>
    <li><strong>Certificate verification</strong> — certificate number or name (not stored)</li>
    <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, browser type, IP address (anonymised)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To contact you about course enquiries and enrolment</li>
    <li>To provide access to your student dashboard and enrolled courses</li>
    <li>To issue and verify course certificates</li>
    <li>To send course updates and announcements (you may opt out any time)</li>
    <li>To improve our website and services</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share it with trusted service providers (such as our database host Supabase) solely to operate our services. We may disclose data if required by law.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
  <p>We use Supabase (ISO 27001 certified infrastructure) with Row Level Security enabled on all tables. HTTPS is enforced on all pages. Passwords are never stored in plain text.</p>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time by emailing us at <a href="mailto:atecgsp@gmail.com">atecgsp@gmail.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use minimal cookies necessary to operate the website (session management). We do not use advertising or tracking cookies.</p>

  <h2>7. Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:atecgsp@gmail.com">atecgsp@gmail.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+917009933289">+91 7009933289</a>.</p>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
